# Hooks & Mutations Rules

## HCM calls

- All HCM HTTP calls must go through `src/lib/hcm-client.ts` (never raw `fetch` in hooks/components).

## Mutation lifecycle (required phases)

- `onMutate`: snapshot + optimistic apply + register in-flight key.
- `mutationFn`: perform write.
- `onSuccess`: canonical re-read and verify; rollback if not confirmed.
- `onError`: rollback snapshot + toast.
- `onSettled`: remove in-flight key; invalidate affected queries.

## Query usage

- Use `queryKeys.*` factories only.
- Avoid multiple `useQuery` calls in the same feature component; split into child components when needed.

